This simple noodle dish is tasty and a lot healthier than takeout. The secret to the noodle dish lies in the actual sauce. That’s why I have created a sauce base that makes these noodles better than your takeout. It’s also a combination of sweet and savoury and that’s what we love most about it. <img class="size-medium wp-image-649983 aligncenter lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/1E75007E-B05D-4103-A912-BDC94B85CA71-897x598.jpeg" alt="" width="897" height="598" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-649985 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/684585D8-C7C2-4603-A3D4-503525DCCCC3.jpeg" alt="" width="1280" height="1264" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/684585D8-C7C2-4603-A3D4-503525DCCCC3.jpeg 1220w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/684585D8-C7C2-4603-A3D4-503525DCCCC3-605x598.jpeg 605w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/684585D8-C7C2-4603-A3D4-503525DCCCC3-1166x1152.jpeg 1166w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/684585D8-C7C2-4603-A3D4-503525DCCCC3-100x100.jpeg 100w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/684585D8-C7C2-4603-A3D4-503525DCCCC3-487x481.jpeg 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/684585D8-C7C2-4603-A3D4-503525DCCCC3-974x962.jpeg 974w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/684585D8-C7C2-4603-A3D4-503525DCCCC3-243x240.jpeg 243w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/684585D8-C7C2-4603-A3D4-503525DCCCC3-486x480.jpeg 486w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/684585D8-C7C2-4603-A3D4-503525DCCCC3-600x593.jpeg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" />